high_descs: Turn around and walk to the large knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn right towards the stove top.
Put the knife in the top drawer to the right of the stove top, to the right of the other knife, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter with the knife on it.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Turn around and go left to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn the water on and then turn it off and pick the knife up.
Turn around and face the drawer to the right of the stove.
Open the drawer to the right of the stove and put the knife in and shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around, head to the counter
Take the yellow knife from the counter
Turn around, head to the sink
Put the knife in the sink, turn on the water for 3 seconds
Take the knife out of the sink, Turn to the right
open the drawer next to the fridge, put the knife in the drawer, close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Wash the yellow knife in the sink, put it in the drawer next to the fridge
